card.note: Dear Adam, you've turned out amazingly decent for a guy who once tried on my underwear. Congratulations on your life's successes.
card.author: Aunt Shan

card.note: I am so proud of you and appreciate all your hard work, sacrifice and dedication. I admire your will, determination and sense of humor through it all! I love you and feel so blessed to have been a part of this journey! Congratulations to my favorite Anesthesiologist!
card.author: Kate

card.note: Hello Adam..... This is a HUGE congratulations to you on your accomplishment in graduating in Anesthesia. You have made us all so very PROUD of your dedication and achievement. You make us look good... ;-)/RI love you and hope to see you and your family SOON!/R
card.author: Aunt Kelly

card.note: You are the best daddy! I am proud of you! I love you!
card.author: Jackson

card.note: I love you!
card.author: Ruby

card.note: Congratulations Daddy! I love you! You are the best Daddy ever!
card.author: Staley

card.note: Hey Adam, Congratulations on your graduation! What an amazing accomplishment for you and your family. I wish you the best of luck as you get into your career and hope you enjoy everyday doing what you love to do. I appreciate your love and example. Love you man!
card.author: Levi Erickson

card.note: Adam, you have accomplished something larger than most people ever pull off in their lives. Amazing job!!! And thanks for being a great guy!
card.author: David and Angie

card.note: Congratulations on graduating, Dr. Adam!!! Hooray! You're my favorite anesthesiologist in the whole history of mankind! Thanks for being such a great brother and friend! I'm so proud of you and love you and Kate so much!! You rock!!
card.author: Jen and the Morley Family

card.note: Adam, since you were born I knew you were an extraordinary person with a strong body, mind, and spirit. You have proved yourself to be exactly that. I have been proud to be your mom in every accomplishment you have achieved, and am even more so at this time. I love you!
card.author: Mom

card.note: Hey Adam, and a big Um Brother to you!/RWould like to tell you how proud I am of you and this accomplishment. You had a dream and you succeeded. God has blessed you with great talents a beautiful wife and family. May you have continued success! Lets go golf! Love you
card.author: Peay

card.note: Adam, You are seriously one of the most generous people I know!! We wish you nothing but the best and I hope you know how proud we are of you!! You will make the most amazing doctor! We sure love you! xoxo
card.author: The Meier's in St Geezy ;-)

card.note: Adam! Congratulations! You've worked so hard for so long and have been so successful! Only more success and great things ahead! We love you!
card.author: Korbin, Allison & Kids

card.note: Hey dude! Congrats on graduating for the tenth time! Just kidding. I'm proud of you, and I'm grateful to have you as an older brother who set a good example for me. I've always looked up to you, and have tried to emulate everything that you've done. Love you
card.author: Spencer

card.note: We are so proud of you! No one ever worked harder to gain a highly skilled education while caring for his family. You have succeeded on every front. We send our love and congratulations.
card.author: Don and Cyndy

card.note: Congrats, Adam! You have worked so hard and we are so proud of you! It's only taken about 15 yrs, but you can finally get a job! I know from experience that you DO have good bedside manner. You can get me RX for pain now, right?! You are awesome and we love you tons!
card.author: Emmie, Eric and Kiddos

card.note: Hey man I just wanted to say how proud I am of you! See what you can accomplish when you listen to your uncle Gold?! :-) Seriously Adam I love you so much and I could't be happier for you, Kate and the kid's. You are a good man and a great father. All my love,
card.author: Golden

card.note: Congratulations on another outstanding achievement and thanks for being such a great example of courage and determination! I know that the path you are on has not been easy, but you have never been one to say "I can't"; you just do whatever you put your mind to....
card.author: Dad

card.note: ...Most importantly, I am grateful that you are such a wonderful father and husband. A parent could never hope for more from their son./RI love you!/R
card.author: Dad

card.note: Hey Babe, You're so close to the finish line and we are there as a family cheering you on. I love you so much and I am so proud of you. I know that Grandma is with me in this. You've made all the right decisions with Heavenly Father and Kate at your side. All my love.
card.author: Gramps
